f=Engineering/ops/custom/platform-playbooks/assets/platform-playbook-template.md · h1:Platform Playbook [platform name] [business name]=One platform, one playbook, one date. Ground truth (verified records) outranks vendor docs. Never edit fiction re-date verification, archive platform change. **As of:** [YYYY-MM-DD] **Source:** [vendor docs version verified-by-doing record refs] **Staleness horizon:** [date past this, use carries "verify before trusting" flag] **Stack-profile section:** [§ref ADR trail platform] **Connector:** [MCP/connector name bound "none manual mechanics below, degraded loudly"] · h2:Deploy mechanics (consumed release-discipline)=Build/artifact: [commands/pipeline verified [date]], Deploy strategies available here: [blue-green/canary/rolling which platform supports, how], Rollback mechanics: [exact procedure thing release-discipline exercises staging], Health checks: [endpoints/probes] · h2:Observability (consumed maintenance-hygiene, incident-response)=Logs live at: [where, retention], Metrics/dashboards: [where; baseline sources], Alerting: [product, thresholds set] · h2:Backups (consumed by maintenance-hygiene)=Service/mechanism: [what backs what], Restore procedure: [exact steps what restore test runs] · h2:Access & limits=Environments: [staging/prod topology], Quotas/limits bite: [dated facts], Expiring items platform: expiry register entries] · h2:Charter notes=Steps playbook touch data destructively: [each written prepared-script-for-OPERATOR playbook never instructs agent run one (Rail 3)], Egress platform's tooling needs: allowlist entries, operator-approved (Rail 2)] · h2:Verified-run log (ground truth re-dates playbook)=\| Date \| Operation \| Record ref \| Playbook section confirmed/corrected \| · h2:Verified-run log (ground truth re-dates playbook)=\|---\|---\|---\|---\|